'''何賽·費南德茲'''（{{Lang-es|'''José D. Fernández'''}}，{{bd|1992年|7月31日|2016年|9月25日|catIDX = Fernández, José}}），是一位古巴裔美国籍的职业棒球员，曾效力於[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]][[邁阿密馬林魚隊|邁阿密馬林魚隊]]，守备位置为[[投手|投手]]，右投右打，為2013年國家聯盟新人王並二度入選明星賽（2013、2016年）。

2016年9月25日，费尔南德斯在发生于迈阿密海滩因自身酒駕超速造成的船难事故中遇难，得年24岁。<ref name="Fernandez ESPN">{{cite web|title=Jose Fernandez dies in boating accident|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/17632541/miami-marlins-ace-jose-fernandez-dies-boating-accident|publisher=ESPN|date=September 25, 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925133154/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/17632541/miami-marlins-ace-jose-fernandez-dies-boating-accident|archivedate=2016-09-25|deadurl=no|accessdate=September 25, 2016}}</ref>驗屍報告也指出，在他體內還驗出了非法毒品[[古柯鹼|古柯鹼]]。

2016年9月26日，馬林魚球團老闆{{link-en|傑佛瑞·羅瑞亞|Jeffrey Loria}}宣布將其16號球衣[[永久欠番|永久退休]]。

==早期生涯==
費南德茲出生於[[古巴|古巴]][[聖克拉拉|聖克拉拉]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360728128 |title=Diaz's homer helps Cardinals beat Marlins and Fernández, 5–4 |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=July 28, 2016 |accessdate=July 29, 2016 |publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |archive-date=2016-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729100617/http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360728128 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。自2005年起，费尔南德斯3次尝试[[偷渡|偷渡]]，均以失败告终。2008年，费尔南德斯与起母亲和妹妹一同乘坐偷渡艇试图第四次偷渡。途中母亲不慎跌入海水中，费尔南德斯跳入海中并将母亲救起。最终一家人顺利逃亡至美国，并定居在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕市]]。<ref name=foxsports>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxsportsflorida.com/mlb/miami-marlins/story/Jose-Fernandez-set-to-make-MLB-debut-Sun?blockID=888847&feedID=3720 |first=Charlie |last=McCarthy |title=Jose Fernandez set to make MLB debut Sunday |work=Fox Sports Florida |date=January 17, 2013 |accessdate=April 6, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/news/jose-fernandez-the-american-dream-172335052.html|title=Jose Fernandez: The American Dream|authorlink=Jeff Passan|work={{link-en|Yahoo! Sports|Yahoo! Sports}}|date=September 25, 2016|accessdate=September 25, 2016|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629081123/https://sports.yahoo.com/news/jose-fernandez-the-american-dream-172335052.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

定居美国后，费尔南德斯进入佛罗里达州的{{link-en|布拉乌里奥·阿隆索高中|Braulio Alonso High School}}，<ref name=tb>{{cite web|url=http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/former-alonso-p-jose-fernandez-anchors-minor-league-no-hitter/13622/|title=Florida high school sports | Former Alonso P Jose Fernández anchors minor league no-hitter|work=Tampa Bay Times|date=April 24, 2012|accessdate=April 5, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222234949/http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/former-alonso-p-jose-fernandez-anchors-minor-league-no-hitter/13622/|archivedate=2014年2月22日}}</ref>并以该校棒球队队员身份参加高中棒球比赛，期间，费尔南德斯曾有三次[[无安打比赛|无安打比赛]]的记录。<ref name=signed>{{cite news|url=http://www.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110815&content_id=23266178&vkey=news_fla&c_id=mia|title=Marlins reach deal with top Draft pick Jose Fernandez|publisher=Major League Baseball|date=August 15, 2011|accessdate=April 6, 2013}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==職業生涯==
===选秀和小联盟时期===
[[File:IMG_0005_José_Fernández.jpg|200px]]
在2011年的MLB选秀中，19岁的费尔南德斯在第一轮第14顺位被佛罗里达马林鱼队（现迈阿密马林鱼）选中，由此开始了职业生涯。<ref name=tb>{{cite web|url=http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/former-alonso-p-jose-fernandez-anchors-minor-league-no-hitter/13622/|title=Florida high school sports | Former Alonso P Jose Fernández anchors minor league no-hitter|work=Tampa Bay Times|date=April 24, 2012|accessdate=April 5, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222234949/http://www.tampabay.com/hometeam/blog/former-alonso-p-jose-fernandez-anchors-minor-league-no-hitter/13622/|archivedate=2014年2月22日}}</ref>之后，费尔南德斯进入了马林鱼队伞下的詹姆斯敦扰乱者队（[[美國職棒小聯盟#紐約─賓夕弗尼亞聯盟（New_York─Pennsylvania_League）|短期1A/纽约-宾夕法尼亚联盟]]）。<ref name=milb2016>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160925&content_id=203283806&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|title=Fernandez stood out in brief Minors career: Marlins' 2011 first-round pick remembered as 'truly one of a kind'|first=Tyler|last=Maun|work=MiLB.com|date=September 25, 2016|accessdate=September 25, 2016|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207135647/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160925&content_id=203283806&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，费尔南德斯被升入格林斯波罗蚱蜢队（[[美國職棒小聯盟#南大西洋聯盟（South_Atlantic_League）|1A/南大西洋联盟]]）。在此期间，费尔南德斯不仅被选中参加MLB明日之星赛，<ref>{{cite web|last=Mayo|first=Jonathan|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120620&content_id=33663130&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|title=Prospects pack rosters for 2012 All-Star Futures Game|work=MLB.com|date=March 12, 2013|accessdate=April 5, 2013|archive-date=2012-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623075429/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120620&content_id=33663130&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>并且以14胜1败，[[防御率|防御率]]1.75和158次[[三振|三振]]的优秀成绩成为了该季马林鱼伞下小联盟球队的最佳投手。<ref>{{cite news|last=Rodriguez|first=Juan C.|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2012-09-29/sports/fl-miami-marlins-0930-20120929_1_tampa-alonso-high-school-christian-yelich-marlins-park|title=Marlins recognize top minor leaguers Yelich, Fernandez|work=Sun Sentinel|date=September 29, 2012|accessdate=April 5, 2013|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610215000/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2012-09-29/sports/fl-miami-marlins-0930-20120929_1_tampa-alonso-high-school-christian-yelich-marlins-park|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====2013賽季：年度最佳新秀====
早在2013年以前，在最有潛力的新秀排名中，{{link-en|美國棒球雜誌|Baseball America}}就已經將費南德茲列為馬林魚隊中的第一名，同時也是全大聯盟第五。<ref>{{cite web|last=Bailey|first=James|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2013/2614456.html|title=Marlins top 2013 prospects|publisher=Baseball America|date=December 12, 2012|accessdate=April 5, 2013|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201081720/https://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2013/2614456.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2013/2614739.html|title=2013 Top 100 Prospects|publisher=Baseball America|date=February 19, 2013|accessdate=April 5, 2013|archive-date=2013-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215184542/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2013/2614739.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>馬林魚邀請了費南德茲加入2013年的春訓，卻在賽季開始前將他下放至小聯盟。不過馬林魚最後在[[納坦·艾瓦爾迪|內森·艾爾瓦迪]]和{{link-en|亨德森·阿爾瓦雷斯|Henderson Álvarez}}受傷的情況下，還是把費南德茲選入開季25人名單。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/marlins/2013/03/31/jose-fernandez-miami-pitching-prospect-opening-day-roster/2039811/|title=Top Marlins prospect Jose Fernandez added to roster|work=USA Today|date=March 31, 2013|accessdate=April 5, 2013|archive-date=2019-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224093144/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/marlins/2013/03/31/jose-fernandez-miami-pitching-prospect-opening-day-roster/2039811/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而且，馬林魚隊的老闆傑佛瑞·羅瑞亞也希望在經過前一球季的球員大清倉後，把費南德茲升上來可以使他更得到球迷的信任。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/news/sources--marlins-owner-jeffrey-loria-personally-mandated-lineup-change-150755500.html |title=Sources: Marlins owner Jeffrey Loria personally mandated pitching lineup change |website=Sports.yahoo.com |accessdate=September 10, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914061518/http://sports.yahoo.com/news/sources--marlins-owner-jeffrey-loria-personally-mandated-lineup-change-150755500.html |archivedate=2013-09-14 }}</ref>球團為了保護他，將他的投球局數限制在大約150局到170局之間。<ref>{{cite news |last=Frisaro |first=Joe |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/43573534/miami-marlins-call-up-top-prospect-jose-fernandez/ |title=Fernandez called up on whirlwind day of transactions |date=March 31, 2013 |accessdate=December 19, 2016 |archive-date=2016-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221180325/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/43573534/miami-marlins-call-up-top-prospect-jose-fernandez/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

而費南德茲在4月7日首度登上大聯盟先發，面對[[紐約大都會|紐約大都會]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxsportsflorida.com/mlb/miami-marlins/story/Jose-Fernandez-set-to-make-MLB-debut-Sun?blockID=888847&feedID=3720|title=Jose Fernandez set to make MLB debut Sunday|publisher=Fox Sports Florida|date=January 17, 2013|accessdate=April 6, 2013}}</ref> 他投了5局，只被敲出3支安打失1分，而且送出8次三振，他成為繼1916年來第7位在大聯盟處女秀就送出至少8次三振，且年齡在21歲以下的球員。<ref>{{cite web|last=Rodriguez|first=Juan C.|url=http://www.sun-sentinel.com/sports/miami-marlins/fl-marlins-0408-20130407,0,5648677.story|title=New York Mets walk-off Miami Marlins, deny Jose Fernandez win in stellar MLB debut|work=Sun-Sentinel|date=April 7, 2013|accessdate=April 10, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-16|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130616031804/http://www.sun-sentinel.com/sports/miami-marlins/fl-marlins-0408-20130407,0,5648677.story|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 5月27日是他的大聯盟第二次先發。<ref>{{cite news|last=Spencer|first=Clark|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/04/14/3343045/rookie-jose-fernandez-dazzles.html|title=Rookie Jose Fernandez dazzles in Miami Marlins' win over Phillies|work=Miami Herald|date=April 14, 2013|accessdate=April 15, 2013}}</ref>對上光芒雖然吞下敗投，但是「鬼才」教練[[喬·梅登|喬·梅登]]卻在推特上稱讚他說：「費南德茲是我見過最有潛力的年輕球員，以他現在的年紀，以後一定很有成就」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/RaysJoeMaddon/status/340589234765299712|title=Twitter / RaysJoeMaddon: Jose Fernandez might be the|publisher=Twitter|accessdate=September 10, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023161955/https://twitter.com/RaysJoeMaddon/status/340589234765299712|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月6日，費南德茲被選為國聯明星隊的馬林魚隊代表球員，他在第6局登板表現完美，先三振了[[達斯汀·佩德羅亞|達斯汀·佩德羅亞]]，再讓[[米格爾·卡布瑞拉|米格爾·卡布瑞拉]]打成內野飛球出局，最後再三振[[克里斯·戴維斯|克里斯·戴維斯]]，他成為繼[[德懷特·古登|德懷特·古登]]和[[鮑伯·費勒|鮑伯·費勒]]之後，第三位以不到21歲之齡便在明星賽面對前3位打者還送出2次三振的球員。<ref name="Miami Marlins’ Jose Fernandez shines at MLB All-Star Game">{{cite news|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/07/17/3503806/miami-marlins-jose-fernandez-shines.html|title=Miami Marlins' Jose Fernandez shines at MLB All-Star Game|date=July 17, 2013|work=Miami Herald|accessdate=September 2, 2013|archive-date=2014-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102191142/http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/07/17/3503806/miami-marlins-jose-fernandez-shines.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在7月28日面對[[匹茲堡海盜|匹茲堡海盜]]，費南德茲單場投出13次三振，球隊也以3比2拿下勝利。<ref name="victoryPirates">{{cite web|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/07/29/3528317/jose-fernandez-strikes-out-13.html|title=Jose Fernandez strikes out 13 as Marlins take series from Pirates|last=Neal|first=David J.|date=July 29, 2013|work=The Miami Herald|accessdate=August 3, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061129/http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/07/29/3528317/jose-fernandez-strikes-out-13.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 之後在8月3日面對[[克里夫蘭印地安人|克里夫蘭印地安人]]，更投出了14K，他也成為繼2000年後，第6位連兩場出賽皆投出至少13次三振的球員。<ref name="backtoback">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.si.com/2013/08/03/jose-fernandez-miami-marlins-cleveland-indians/|title=A young Jose Fernandez continues to make history in fanning 14 Cleveland Indians|last=Lemire|first=Joe|date=August 3, 2013|work=Sports Illustrated|accessdate=August 3, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805214332/http://mlb.si.com/2013/08/03/jose-fernandez-miami-marlins-cleveland-indians/|archivedate=2013年8月5日}}</ref> 其中更是創下馬林魚單場最多三振的隊史新紀錄，一舉奪得該年7月最佳新人球員的頭銜。<ref name="Fernandez named NL Rookie of the Month for July 2013">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130805&content_id=55975422&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|title=Fernandez named NL Rookie of the Month|date=August 5, 2013|publisher=Major League Baseball|accessdate=August 13, 2013|archive-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817022124/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130805&content_id=55975422&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了8月，他持續著他的好手感，在39局的投球中，他投出49次三振，防禦率僅1.15，他再度拿下該年8月最佳新人球員的榮譽。<ref name="Marlins Jose Fernandez voted National League Rookie of the Month for August">{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130904&content_id=59550722&vkey=pr_mlb&c_id=mlb|title=Marlins Jose Fernandez voted National League Rookie of the Month for August|date=September 4, 2013|publisher=Major League Baseball|accessdate=September 11, 2013|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812162406/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130904&content_id=59550722&vkey=pr_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>

