erboards - Fangraphs">{{cite web|url=http://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=sta&lg=nl&qual=y&type=8&season=2013&month=0&season1=2013&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=9,d|date=September 2, 2013|publisher=FanGraphs|title=National League Leaderboards » 2013 » Starters » Dashboard|accessdate=September 2, 2013|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215171912/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=sta&lg=nl&qual=y&type=8&season=2013&month=0&season1=2013&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=9,d|dead-url=no}}</ref>

