-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140514151032/http://www.miamiherald.com/2014/05/13/4115021/report-jose-fernandez-has-significant.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在5月16日進行湯米·約翰手術。這一年他只先發8場，戰績4勝2敗，防禦率2.44以及投出70次三振。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/baseball/mlb/jose-fernandez-has-tommy-john-surgery-on-pitching-elbow-1.2646102|title=Jose Fernandez has Tommy John surgery on pitching elbow: Attorney for hurler says changed throwing motion led to injury|publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|agency=Associated Press|date=May 16, 2014|accessdate=September 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121081345/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/baseball/mlb/jose-fernandez-has-tommy-john-surgery-on-pitching-elbow-1.2646102|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====2015賽季====
