http://www.miamiherald.com/sports/mlb/miami-marlins/article36647019.html|accessdate=March 9, 2016|work=Miami Herald|date=September 25, 2015|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402113829/https://www.miamiherald.com/sports/mlb/miami-marlins/article36647019.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=350925128|title=Jose Fernandez 1st to win first 17 home decisions as Marlins beat Braves|agency=Associated Press|date=September 25, 2015|accessdate=September 26, 2015|publisher=ESPN|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203125207/http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=350925128|dead-url=no}}</ref>

