==投球風格==
費南德茲的實戰球路以[[四縫線快速球|四縫線快速球]]、[[滑曲球|滑曲球]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fangraphs.com/blogs/jose-fernandez-has-two-breaking-balls/ |title=Jose Fernandez Has Two Breaking Balls {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball、2017年4月11日閱覽 |accessdate=2017年4月11日 |archive-date=2018年12月25日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225102830/https://www.fangraphs.com/blogs/jose-fernandez-has-two-breaking-balls/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[變速球|變速球]]等3種為主，偶爾也會加入稀少的伸卡球與慢速曲球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brooksbaseball.net/landing.php?player=605228|title=Player Card: Jose Fernandez|website=brooksbaseball.net|accessdate=April 9, 2017|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215122311/http://www.brooksbaseball.net/landing.php?player=605228|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中銳利的滑曲球占了全投球的約三分之一比例，為他最倚賴的變化球種。最快球速高達100.2mph<ref name="fg">{{Cite web |url=http://www.fangraphs.com/pitchfx.aspx?playerid=11530&position=P |title=PitchFx » Overview {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball |accessdate=2017-04-09 |archive-date=2018-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181120040603/https://www.fangraphs.com/pitchfx.aspx?playerid=11530&position=P |dead-url=no }}</ref>(161km/h)，平均也能維持在95mph(153km/h)左右於先發投手中的一流水準<ref name="fg"/>。費南德茲不僅具有優秀的球威，也是一個具有控球的三振型投手，MLB生涯三振率(K/9)為11.2，保送率(BB/9)為2.7。

