2016年9月20日，費南德茲在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上宣布女友阿里亞絲（Maria Arias）懷了第一個小孩<ref name=nydn>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/jose-fernandez-marlins-pitcher-killed-boating-accident-article-1.2805674|title=Jose Fernandez, Marlins pitcher, killed in boating accident at 24 years old|work=Daily News|location=New York|first1=Amara|last1=Grautski|first2=Dan|last2=Good|first3=Stephen|last3=Rex Brown|date=September 25, 2016|accessdate=September 25, 2016|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417095653/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/jose-fernandez-marlins-pitcher-killed-boating-accident-article-1.2805674|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===意外驟逝===

2016年9月25日早上3點30分，費南德茲在佛羅里達的邁阿密海灘發現死於船難，在船上也發現另外兩名死者。據信死因是因為駕駛視線不佳而全速衝撞礁岩，導致費南德茲受到船隻嚴重撞擊，<ref name="Fernandez ESPN"/>成為繼2014年[[聖路易紅雀隊|聖路易紅雀隊]]的外野手[[奧斯卡·塔維拉斯|奧斯卡·塔維拉斯]]之後，在球季結束前意外過世的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://redbirdrants.com/2016/09/25/st-louis-cardinals-crying-baseball/|title=St. Louis Cardinals: There is crying in baseball, RIP Jose Fernandez|first=Michael|last=Miles|work=Redbirds Rants|date=September 25, 2016|accessdate=October 9, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221135835/http://redbirdrants.com/2016/09/25/st-louis-cardinals-crying-baseball/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於他的天真、熱情以及對於棒球的熱愛，費南德茲在聯盟中人緣非常好；他過世後整個聯盟頓時陷入悲戚之中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/26/sports/baseball/jose-fernandez-boating-accident-miami-marlins.html|title=After His Despair, Jose Fernandez Forged an Ebullient Life|first=Tyler|last=Kepner|work=The New York Times|date=September 25, 2016|accessdate=October 9, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113151901/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/26/sports/baseball/jose-fernandez-boating-accident-miami-marlins.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>台灣投手[[陳偉殷|陳偉殷]]在內的馬林魚隊員和教練[[丹·馬丁利|丹·馬丁利]]在告別記者會上泣不成聲，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/jose-fernandez-dead-miami-marlins-press-conference-team-break-down-tears-a7330141.html|title=Jose Fernandez dead: Miami Marlins team break down in tears at press conference|first=Maya|last=Oppenheim|work=The Independent|date=September 26, 2016|accessdate=October 9, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131039/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/jose-fernandez-dead-miami-marlins-press-conference-team-break-down-tears-a7330141.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>老爹[[大衛·歐提茲|大衛·歐提茲]]更因過於悲傷而取消在光芒隊主場的退休巡禮，並在默哀致敬中頻頻拭淚。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/boston-red-sox/2016/09/25/david-ortiz-asked-tampa-bay-to-cancel-pregame-tribute-following-death-of-his-friend-jose-fernandez|title=David Ortiz asked Tampa Bay to cancel pregame tribute following death of his friend Jose Fernandez|first=Nik|last=DeCosta-Klipa|work=Boston.com|date=September 26, 2016|accessdate=October 9, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220193058/http://www.boston.com/sports/boston-red-sox/2016/09/25/david-ortiz-asked-tampa-bay-to-cancel-pregame-tribute-following-death-of-his-friend-jose-fernandez|dead-url=no}}</ref>

令人感傷且驚奇的是，美國時間9月26日對大都會的比賽，[[迪·古登|迪·古登]]在比賽首打席帶著費南德茲的頭盔上場，並在第三個球揮出了本季的第一支全壘打。當繞回休息區時，古登撫摸頭盔並痛哭失聲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/27/sports/baseball/dee-gordon-home-run-jose-fernandez.html|title=Dee Gordon Hits His First Home Run of the Year in Tribute to Jose Fernandez|publisher=The New York Times|date=September 26, 2016|accessdate=October 9, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140234/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/27/sports/baseball/dee-gordon-home-run-jose-fernandez.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年10月，Fernandez的驗屍報告指出，在他體內驗出非法毒品古柯鹼和酒精，其血液中的酒精濃度多達.147，約為當地合法標準的近兩倍。2017年3月，船難的調查報告正式出爐，認定為Fernandez酒醉駕船並且超速，造成自己與同行友人身亡，如果他還生還，也會因過失致死罪遭移送法辦。

